"This section allows you to modify the fonts used within the Cell or Header "
"fields."
msgstr "Ove opcije vam omogućavaju da podesite fontove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use system fonts"
msgstr "Koristi fontove sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: details-settings.docbook:1025
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Select this to use system fonts. Deselecting this option allows you to "
#| "customize fonts."
msgid ""
"Select this to use system fonts. Deselecting this option allows you to "
"select the fonts of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite ovo za korištenje fontova sistema. Ukoliko ova opcija nije "
"odabrana, možete podesiti fontove kako vam odgovara."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: details-settings.docbook:1033
